               <p>SECOND COUNT, for feloniously uttering and publishing as true, a like forged promissory note, with the like intent, he knowing it to be forged and counterfeited.</p>
               <p>THIRD AND FOURTH COUNTS, the same, only stating his intent to be to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t18180909-81-victim689" type="victimName">
                     James 
